{"tid":1568430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忍唔到左膠？麻煩大家幫手推","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:27:04.000Z","uid":19945,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a3bb9943138a210168c116c8b4a0ea23c457a6be","tid":1568430,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解到依刻大家仲屌緊<br />\n點解又唔打？又放？又係左膠？<br />\n因為成班係連登圍爐打飛機<br />\n出面無人有個心態係<br />\n唔打叫狗=自殺<br />\n唔明私了=杜絕未來比藍絲打<br />\n左膠=禍害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想依個post係一個契機同大家一齊諗辦法<br />\n真真正正做一場香港人潔癖文宣<br />\n例如一齊將有用既連登post放link上立場蘋果xxxx<br />\n集中like做top comment引人睇<br />\n將私了既comment集中like做top comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要人地一睇comment就睇到<br />\n保護藍絲=助長恐怖主義<br />\n<br />\n你地一味屌無用<br />\n點解勇武可以由幾年前既間諜變英雄<br />\n就係靠文宣配合社會情況改變人<br />\n我地要開始集中做文宣講私了既原因<br />\n唔係出氣禁簡單 大家唔好係連登屌啦<br />\n一齊諗計一齊做香港網絡戰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c413da9626d3bf2a6102d7495ef67a452e7710d","tid":1568430,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c308b97def732ec2a345e80969edfb3719c0b3f1","tid":1568430,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d5ebe91e2b9be27f7880df7fd63daf319ae8be7","tid":1568430,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bc99e9f802f2d5404a10d9cae06c900a269cd6b","tid":1568430,"uid":5031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:46:13.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776c9b9c45b4d4b7a430ff61a46c8e67b5d37fde","tid":1568430,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f6954fff8690a6da00264b587f78d71866a3a0f","tid":1568430,"uid":5430